high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn left again and walk up to the large wooden table.
Pick up the spatula that is in front of the toaster on the large wooden table.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the table.
Put the spatula in the metal pan to the right of the toaster on the table.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it off of the table.
Turn right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Put the metal pan with the spatula in it into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pan with a spatula in it into the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table.
Pick up the spatula from the table.
Move closer to the pan.
Put the spatula in the pan.
Pick up the pan and spatula from the table.
Walk over to the sink.
Put the spatula and pan in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the spatula and pan in the sink to be washed.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table behind you.
Pick up the spatula on the counter top, between the toaster and the knife.
Move over to your right so that you are directly in front of the fry pan that is on the counter and all the way in the back.
Place the spatula into the fry pan that is on the counter and beside the toaster.
Pick up the fry pan with the spatula inside it.
Turn to your right and walk to the sink.
Place the fry pan with the spatula in it, inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a fry pan containing a spatula into the kitchen sink.
